Model overruns past EndLineInc with trailing lines that already match the buffer; processCompletion trims that suffix so it isn't treated as a no-op modification.
row: 2
col: 4
viewportTop: 1
viewportBottom: 20
-- buffer.txt --
def main():
    pass
    foo
    bar
-- steps --
completion 2-2
  | "    x = 1"
  | "    foo"
  | "    bar"
expect shown
  buffer:
    | "def main():"
    | "    x = 1"
    | "    foo"
    | "    bar"

